This pull request only partially resolves the problem.

We need to change `TableWriter` class like below.

current :
https://github.com/PowerShell/PowerShell/blob/9bc81ad695c7eba777255a2905aec58adc90daa1/src/System.Management.Automation/FormatAndOutput/common/TableWriter.cs#L292-L310

after change (example):

```csharp
            // add padding for the columns that are shorter
            for (int col = 0; col < scArray.Length; col++)
            {
                int paddingBlanks = _si.columnInfo[validColumnArray[col]].width;
                if (col > 0)
                    paddingBlanks += ScreenInfo.separatorCharacterCount;
                else
                {
                    paddingBlanks += _startColumn;
                }
                int paddingEntries = screenRows - scArray[col].Count;
                if (paddingEntries > 0)
                {
                    for (int j = 0; j < paddingEntries; j++)
                    {
                        scArray[col].Add(col == scArray.Length - 1 ? "" : StringUtil.Padding(paddingBlanks));
                    }
                }
            }
```
